➜华为 Mate40 Pro 测评：对比 iPhone 12 Pro，你关心的都在这里
https://www.ifanr.com/1375632?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	29199
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375723" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mate40-pro.png" alt="" width="1734" height="974" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mate40-pro.png 1734w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mate40-pro-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mate40-pro-768x431.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mate40-pro-1024x575.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1734px) 100vw, 1734px" /></p>
<p>作为华为下半年最重磅的产品，Mate 系列手机可以说「出生自带光环」。</p>
<p>在经历 8 年 10 代的探索后，华为终于在上周发布了 Mate40 系列——「中杯」、「大杯」、「超大杯」，一应俱全。</p>
<p>这次，爱范儿在第一时间拿到了「大杯」Mate40 Pro。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375633" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0a43ad22-bcd3-4abd-9646-2673189e4ecf.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0a43ad22-bcd3-4abd-9646-2673189e4ecf.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0a43ad22-bcd3-4abd-9646-2673189e4ecf-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0a43ad22-bcd3-4abd-9646-2673189e4ecf-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/0a43ad22-bcd3-4abd-9646-2673189e4ecf-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p><strong>和 Mate30 Pro 相比，这一代在外观上的变化还是很容易发现的。</strong></p>
<p>首先，机身尺寸大了一圈，屏幕尺寸从 6.53 英寸来到了 6.76 英寸。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375636" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4ca49cdb-0b7d-4004-95a3-f72d9e8cbbde.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4ca49cdb-0b7d-4004-95a3-f72d9e8cbbde.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4ca49cdb-0b7d-4004-95a3-f72d9e8cbbde-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4ca49cdb-0b7d-4004-95a3-f72d9e8cbbde-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4ca49cdb-0b7d-4004-95a3-f72d9e8cbbde-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>其次，正脸的「刘海」设计，变成了一颗圆滑的「药丸」。这种圆滑也体现在了机身上，Mate30 Pro 的顶部和底部是被削平的，而 Mate40 Pro 则是有弧度的。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375663" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d6e81cde-20a6-4a2d-ba7f-0ebf6410946a.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d6e81cde-20a6-4a2d-ba7f-0ebf6410946a.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d6e81cde-20a6-4a2d-ba7f-0ebf6410946a-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d6e81cde-20a6-4a2d-ba7f-0ebf6410946a-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d6e81cde-20a6-4a2d-ba7f-0ebf6410946a-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>理论上，这种设计在单手操作时对小拇指更友好，但 212 克的重量，还是打破了我们的幻想。</p>
<p>背面来看，Mate40 Pro 保留了上一代极具辨识度的「奥利奥」设计，只不过把摄像头和闪光灯，统一放到了外圈，这被华为称作「星环设计」。在 Pro 星环里的四个圆圈，有三颗是摄像头，右上方的则是一颗激光对焦传感器。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375644" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20e0e202-d6b1-47e4-99e0-7872b16419b0.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20e0e202-d6b1-47e4-99e0-7872b16419b0.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20e0e202-d6b1-47e4-99e0-7872b16419b0-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20e0e202-d6b1-47e4-99e0-7872b16419b0-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/20e0e202-d6b1-47e4-99e0-7872b16419b0-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>和上一代相比，广角摄像头，也就是主摄，从 4000 万像素提升到 5000 万，传感器尺寸也增大至 1/1.28 英寸，理论上可以带来更好的暗光表现。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375645" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/62c84990-16e2-4352-b715-c429c973b120.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/62c84990-16e2-4352-b715-c429c973b120.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/62c84990-16e2-4352-b715-c429c973b120-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/62c84990-16e2-4352-b715-c429c973b120-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/62c84990-16e2-4352-b715-c429c973b120-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>但可惜的是，OIS 光学防抖被「刀」掉了，留给了「超大杯」和保时捷设计版。</p>
<p>对比来看，Mate40 Pro 的主摄拍摄效果比上一代提升还是比较明显的，色彩更加讨喜，放大后的细节也更丰富。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375657" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/08679822-81cb-4217-a042-c2d909c58bf5.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/08679822-81cb-4217-a042-c2d909c58bf5.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/08679822-81cb-4217-a042-c2d909c58bf5-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/08679822-81cb-4217-a042-c2d909c58bf5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/08679822-81cb-4217-a042-c2d909c58bf5-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>超广角电影摄像头的像素，虽然从 4000 万缩水到 2000 万，最大光圈也从 f/1.6 缩小至 f/1.8。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375654" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/224855a8-af04-4b18-bcb2-39b200590e6b.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/224855a8-af04-4b18-bcb2-39b200590e6b.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/224855a8-af04-4b18-bcb2-39b200590e6b-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/224855a8-af04-4b18-bcb2-39b200590e6b-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/224855a8-af04-4b18-bcb2-39b200590e6b-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>但在实拍表现上，Mate40 Pro 还是稳赢了上一代，从边缘处的噪点控制、细节表现等方面都可以看出来。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375666" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e20d529c-fd56-4789-8003-63e58dffbc57.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e20d529c-fd56-4789-8003-63e58dffbc57.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e20d529c-fd56-4789-8003-63e58dffbc57-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e20d529c-fd56-4789-8003-63e58dffbc57-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e20d529c-fd56-4789-8003-63e58dffbc57-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>不过这一代的抗畸变算法，呈现的效果似乎没有 Mate30 Pro 那么好，这让我们有点摸不着头脑。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375640" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9aeba588-3e59-43b4-bf81-3e54a1b0f3a5.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9aeba588-3e59-43b4-bf81-3e54a1b0f3a5.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9aeba588-3e59-43b4-bf81-3e54a1b0f3a5-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9aeba588-3e59-43b4-bf81-3e54a1b0f3a5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9aeba588-3e59-43b4-bf81-3e54a1b0f3a5-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>长焦镜头由 800 万像素升级到 1200 万（潜望式），依然支持光学防抖，可以实现 5 倍光学变焦、10 倍混合变焦和 50 倍数字变焦。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375646" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/67fa0758-cd06-4860-b748-616c4ed72d24.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/67fa0758-cd06-4860-b748-616c4ed72d24.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/67fa0758-cd06-4860-b748-616c4ed72d24-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/67fa0758-cd06-4860-b748-616c4ed72d24-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/67fa0758-cd06-4860-b748-616c4ed72d24-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>两代机型对比来看，明显看出 Mate40 Pro 的画面更锐利，涂抹感较少。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375641" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9e8105de-43f3-400a-8201-84cce845d4b2.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9e8105de-43f3-400a-8201-84cce845d4b2.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9e8105de-43f3-400a-8201-84cce845d4b2-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9e8105de-43f3-400a-8201-84cce845d4b2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9e8105de-43f3-400a-8201-84cce845d4b2-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p><strong>除了外观上的变化，Mate40 Pro 的升级点还体现在芯片和快充上。</strong></p>
<p>Mate40 Pro 搭载了华为首块以 4 位数命名的麒麟 9000 芯片。主要看点在于 5nm 制程工艺、第三代 5G 技术 、8 核 CPU 、24 核 GPU 以及 NPU 的组合。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375639" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8fdfb4f2-e9c7-42b7-9351-b9c4aa1ebf52.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8fdfb4f2-e9c7-42b7-9351-b9c4aa1ebf52.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8fdfb4f2-e9c7-42b7-9351-b9c4aa1ebf52-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8fdfb4f2-e9c7-42b7-9351-b9c4aa1ebf52-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8fdfb4f2-e9c7-42b7-9351-b9c4aa1ebf52-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>但由于系统限制，我们目前还无法对其进行跑分测试。根据外媒 GSMaren 发布的数据来看，Mate40 Pro 在 GeekBench 5 的跑分测试中，麒麟 9000 毫无压力地成为当前安卓阵营中最强的手机芯片。关于更详细的跑分数据，我们还需等待系统开放权限后再做测试。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375638" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8b9741e7-b69c-4795-ab90-1ac113fea1bb.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8b9741e7-b69c-4795-ab90-1ac113fea1bb.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8b9741e7-b69c-4795-ab90-1ac113fea1bb-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8b9741e7-b69c-4795-ab90-1ac113fea1bb-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/8b9741e7-b69c-4795-ab90-1ac113fea1bb-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375658" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ab2df33d-0c37-431a-a873-e57792c841b4.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ab2df33d-0c37-431a-a873-e57792c841b4.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ab2df33d-0c37-431a-a873-e57792c841b4-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ab2df33d-0c37-431a-a873-e57792c841b4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/ab2df33d-0c37-431a-a873-e57792c841b4-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>这颗芯片在游戏的表现上如何呢？我们使用了画面质量较好的《原神》来进行测试，通过电脑端实时输出帧率。我们把游戏画面质量调至最高，Mate40 Pro 在 20 分钟左右的游戏中，平均帧率为 43.3 FPS，能维持在 60 FPS 的时长比较短。不过实际体验中，是没有卡顿感的，一直比较流畅。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375669" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uw5c14xsRJkncveS__thumbnail.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uw5c14xsRJkncveS__thumbnail.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uw5c14xsRJkncveS__thumbnail-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uw5c14xsRJkncveS__thumbnail-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/uw5c14xsRJkncveS__thumbnail-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>在充电速度上，Mate40 Pro 从前代的 40W 有线充电、27W 无线充电，升级为 66W 有线快充和 50W 无线快充。实测充电时长为 50 分钟左右（*有线充电）。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375662" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d2bbc448-d222-41c3-b5d2-255437fa2f8f.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d2bbc448-d222-41c3-b5d2-255437fa2f8f.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d2bbc448-d222-41c3-b5d2-255437fa2f8f-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d2bbc448-d222-41c3-b5d2-255437fa2f8f-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d2bbc448-d222-41c3-b5d2-255437fa2f8f-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>对比 Mate30 Pro，Mate40 Pro 还升级了防误触算法，这几天的使用中，感受还是比较明显的。躺着刷微博，页面终于不会乱跳了。</p>
<p>另外升级的 AI 隔空操控，其实是一个平时用不到，但一用就很香的功能。比如我们在厨房做饭时，一定不想用沾满油渍的手来拿手机，这时候只需要将手悬停在屏幕上方，就可以唤醒它查看信息。如果要接电话，隔空按压一下就可以，实测成功率还是挺高的。还有一些深度的手势操控，但对普通人来说学习成本就有点高了。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375661" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/c5b82b23-1946-419a-97ce-9c32b3bb2fc6.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/c5b82b23-1946-419a-97ce-9c32b3bb2fc6.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/c5b82b23-1946-419a-97ce-9c32b3bb2fc6-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/c5b82b23-1946-419a-97ce-9c32b3bb2fc6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/c5b82b23-1946-419a-97ce-9c32b3bb2fc6-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>另外值得关注的就是 EMUI 11 带来的一些新特性，比如多屏协同的升级、更美观的 UI 页面等，我们此前有专门讲解过（《「华为 EMUI 11 体验：我终于可以不在手机、电脑间反复横跳》），在这里就不做赘述了。</p>
<p><strong>在拿到 Mate40 Pro 之后，我们征集了很多读者的问题，发现大家还是比较关心它与 iPhone 12 Pro 相比，谁更能打。尤其是影像能力、信号、4G 和 5G 的网速、续航等等。</strong></p>
<p>在影像能力方面，我们分别在光线充足和光线较弱的环境下，来测试 Mate40 Pro 和 iPhone 12 Pro 的拍照水平。</p>
<p>先来看主摄镜头，在光线充足的环境下，Mate40 Pro 凭借着大底的优势，解析力要更好。不过色温似乎有些偏冷，整体有点发绿。 iPhone 12 Pro 的色彩更真实一些。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375664" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d78bf517-5174-4232-a236-83f6e50ba940.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d78bf517-5174-4232-a236-83f6e50ba940.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d78bf517-5174-4232-a236-83f6e50ba940-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d78bf517-5174-4232-a236-83f6e50ba940-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/d78bf517-5174-4232-a236-83f6e50ba940-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>在人像模式下，iPhone 12 Pro 对人物边缘的处理要稍好些，但差距不大。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375667" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/fe14bb61-9f28-4e44-b240-dac15fae038d.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/fe14bb61-9f28-4e44-b240-dac15fae038d.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/fe14bb61-9f28-4e44-b240-dac15fae038d-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/fe14bb61-9f28-4e44-b240-dac15fae038d-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/fe14bb61-9f28-4e44-b240-dac15fae038d-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>在光线较暗的情况下，若两者都不开启夜景模式，Mate40 Pro 的主摄画面整体亮度更高，噪点更少，放大后的细节也比 iPhone 好不少。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375643" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/17cffdbc-efd9-4a55-ab1b-fc736b005d87.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/17cffdbc-efd9-4a55-ab1b-fc736b005d87.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/17cffdbc-efd9-4a55-ab1b-fc736b005d87-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/17cffdbc-efd9-4a55-ab1b-fc736b005d87-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/17cffdbc-efd9-4a55-ab1b-fc736b005d87-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>开启夜景模式后，两者的算法差异进一步拉开。同一场景下，Mate40 Pro 默认的曝光时长为 10 秒左右，这使得最终的画面非常亮，像是白天一样。而 iPhone 12 Pro 的曝光时长只有三秒，画面依旧保持着夜晚的氛围。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375665" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e02ad9d2-3cf4-4895-a3f9-aee6a2a39d50.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e02ad9d2-3cf4-4895-a3f9-aee6a2a39d50.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e02ad9d2-3cf4-4895-a3f9-aee6a2a39d50-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e02ad9d2-3cf4-4895-a3f9-aee6a2a39d50-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/e02ad9d2-3cf4-4895-a3f9-aee6a2a39d50-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375660" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/b349ec7e-8dda-48a8-bace-ab721108c8a1.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/b349ec7e-8dda-48a8-bace-ab721108c8a1.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/b349ec7e-8dda-48a8-bace-ab721108c8a1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/b349ec7e-8dda-48a8-bace-ab721108c8a1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/b349ec7e-8dda-48a8-bace-ab721108c8a1-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>这很好的体现了两者对于夜景模式的逻辑，一个是追求更亮，一个则是追求真实，哪一种更好见仁见智。另外我们发现，如果手动减少 Mate40 Pro 的曝光时间至 5 秒，那么呈现的画面就可以在丰富细节的基础上，保留夜晚的氛围。</p>
<p>在夜晚的拍照测试时，我们发现 Mate40 Pro 的「鬼影」现象，比 iPhone 12 Pro 要轻一些。这可能和镜头镀膜、排布有关。</p>
<p>再来看超广角镜头，两者的焦段不同，iPhone 12 Pro 的明显要更广。在画面质量上，无论是解析力，还是画面纯净度，Mate40 Pro 还是要更好一些。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375634" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1d6999cc-2bdb-4e74-9df4-5afb9f835608.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1d6999cc-2bdb-4e74-9df4-5afb9f835608.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1d6999cc-2bdb-4e74-9df4-5afb9f835608-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1d6999cc-2bdb-4e74-9df4-5afb9f835608-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1d6999cc-2bdb-4e74-9df4-5afb9f835608-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>在暗光环境下，Mate40 Pro 对于噪点的控制稳胜 iPhone 12 Pro。不过 iPhone 12 Pro 对于现场亮度的还原要更真实。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375642" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9fa5e5f1-8541-4b2a-9ee5-b9a3334cfc7f.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9fa5e5f1-8541-4b2a-9ee5-b9a3334cfc7f.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9fa5e5f1-8541-4b2a-9ee5-b9a3334cfc7f-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9fa5e5f1-8541-4b2a-9ee5-b9a3334cfc7f-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/9fa5e5f1-8541-4b2a-9ee5-b9a3334cfc7f-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>夜景模式下，两者的画面亮度进一步提高，不过 iPhone 12 Pro 还是维持在较低的亮度。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375651" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1791c5c3-9f20-4623-a368-9406e1d6c079.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1791c5c3-9f20-4623-a368-9406e1d6c079.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1791c5c3-9f20-4623-a368-9406e1d6c079-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1791c5c3-9f20-4623-a368-9406e1d6c079-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1791c5c3-9f20-4623-a368-9406e1d6c079-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>长焦镜头方面，两者其实没有对比的必要。因为 Mate40 Pro 支持 5 倍光学变焦，而 iPhone 12 Pro 则是 2 倍。在光线充足的情况下，两者的长焦画质都比较可观。不过在光线较弱时，Mate40 Pro 会在光学变焦和数码变焦之间反复横跳，iPhone 12 Pro 的情况会好一些。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375655" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3208772f-0f32-48df-97a8-d8979b0fcad1.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3208772f-0f32-48df-97a8-d8979b0fcad1.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3208772f-0f32-48df-97a8-d8979b0fcad1-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3208772f-0f32-48df-97a8-d8979b0fcad1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/3208772f-0f32-48df-97a8-d8979b0fcad1-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>在对焦速度上，Mate40 Pro 有一个激光对焦模组，iPhone 12 Pro 的激光雷达扫描仪也会辅助对焦。我们在低光环境下测试了一下两者的对焦速度，Mate40 Pro 显得更干脆一些。</p>
<p>Mate40 Pro 的前置镜头为 1300 万像素，iPhone 12 Pro 是 1200 万。两者的自拍效果，差异还是比较明显的。Mate40 Pro 的画面比 iPhone 12 Pro 更亮一点。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375648" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90a796d9-1b6d-45fb-8f82-266a740a6317.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90a796d9-1b6d-45fb-8f82-266a740a6317.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90a796d9-1b6d-45fb-8f82-266a740a6317-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90a796d9-1b6d-45fb-8f82-266a740a6317-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/90a796d9-1b6d-45fb-8f82-266a740a6317-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 小姐姐表示，她更喜欢 iPhone 12 Pro 的肤色，看起来更自然。</p>
</div>
<p>视频拍摄方面，两者都最高支持拍摄 4K 60 帧的影像。不过 iPhone 12 Pro 支持杜比视界 HDR 拍摄，这一点 Mate40 Pro 很难打得过，即便 Mate40 Pro 的硬件支持实时 HDR 了。可以看到 iPhone 12 Pro 在细节、色彩还原等方面都做得更好，但遗憾的是，在室内灯光下容易出现频闪。</p>
<p>在防抖方面，iPhone 12 Pro 更优秀，能给人一种很顺滑的感觉。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375650" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/979d19bc-2075-44bb-9634-3ba7e9370127.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/979d19bc-2075-44bb-9634-3ba7e9370127.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/979d19bc-2075-44bb-9634-3ba7e9370127-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/979d19bc-2075-44bb-9634-3ba7e9370127-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/979d19bc-2075-44bb-9634-3ba7e9370127-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>不过在可玩性上，Mate40 Pro 要更强一些。通过算法实现的 AI 跟拍功能，可以让选中的主角始终保持在画面中心。再比如可以同时打开前后摄像头，同时记录前后两个画面。</p>
<p>总结来看，在拍照方面，Mate40 Pro 的上限会更高，但在摄像方面，还是 iPhone 12 Pro 更强。</p>
<p>信号方面，华为的能力毋庸置疑，妥妥的信号标杆。我们更关心的是两者的网络速度如何。我们用一张联通 4G 卡、联通 5G 卡、电信 5G 卡，分别对两台手机的联网速率进行了测试。</p>
<p>我们将每张卡在每台手机上测试两次，然后取平均数来确定速率。结果显示，今年换用高通基带的 iPhone 12 Pro，与 Mate40 Pro 不分伯仲。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375752" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jjj.png" alt="" width="1770" height="496" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jjj.png 1770w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jjj-360x101.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jjj-768x215.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/jjj-1024x287.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1770px) 100vw, 1770px" /></p>
<p>最后，我们来看看两者的续航情况。Mate40 Pro 的电池容量为 4400mAh（典型值），而 iPhone 12 Pro 只有 2815mAh。需要说明的是，测试时 Mate40 Pro 的刷新率设置为「智能」，意思就是会自动在 60Hz 与 90Hz 之间智能切换。另外它的屏幕尺寸也比 iPhone 12 Pro 要大了 0.66 英寸。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375635" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4a5c6862-f709-4d20-9e98-969dd012bcc2.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4a5c6862-f709-4d20-9e98-969dd012bcc2.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4a5c6862-f709-4d20-9e98-969dd012bcc2-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4a5c6862-f709-4d20-9e98-969dd012bcc2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/4a5c6862-f709-4d20-9e98-969dd012bcc2-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>我们很好奇实际使用中，两者的差距如何。我们将两台手机连入同一个 WiFi，亮度控制在 80%，音量调至中等，展开了两小时的续航测试。</p>
<p>测试结果上，Mate40 Pro 的续航相对更优秀，但两者的差距并不算大。有些环节 iPhone 12 Pro 的表现还要更好。</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375659" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/add0e047-e56f-4b92-9b6c-9c0725d86ae0.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/add0e047-e56f-4b92-9b6c-9c0725d86ae0.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/add0e047-e56f-4b92-9b6c-9c0725d86ae0-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/add0e047-e56f-4b92-9b6c-9c0725d86ae0-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/add0e047-e56f-4b92-9b6c-9c0725d86ae0-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375649" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/115ce981-e996-426a-9d57-f5fd95424408.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/115ce981-e996-426a-9d57-f5fd95424408.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/115ce981-e996-426a-9d57-f5fd95424408-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/115ce981-e996-426a-9d57-f5fd95424408-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/115ce981-e996-426a-9d57-f5fd95424408-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
<p>当然，以上的测试项目，并不能说明两款产品谁更好，大家在选购一台手机时需要更多角度的考虑，比如价格。</p>
<p>整体来说，Mate40 Pro 是一款各方面都比较均衡的机器。虽然相比上一代，在参数上没有飞跃，但却把短板都补齐了，比如高刷屏、快充等等，在体验上的进步还是比较明显的。这种体验至上的价值取向，我们相信比激进地追求参数，要来得更为实用。</p>
<p>好了，以上就是本期华为 Mate40 Pro 评测的全部内容了，喜欢的话欢迎分享~</p>
<p><strong>福利放送：</strong></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375647" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/75eb6e6c-3d70-4dff-8835-19039ae3988f.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/75eb6e6c-3d70-4dff-8835-19039ae3988f.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/75eb6e6c-3d70-4dff-8835-19039ae3988f-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/75eb6e6c-3d70-4dff-8835-19039ae3988f-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/75eb6e6c-3d70-4dff-8835-19039ae3988f-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375637" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/07c9f517-67c7-4782-a685-fd8fab3fbf5a.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/07c9f517-67c7-4782-a685-fd8fab3fbf5a.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/07c9f517-67c7-4782-a685-fd8fab3fbf5a-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/07c9f517-67c7-4782-a685-fd8fab3fbf5a-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/07c9f517-67c7-4782-a685-fd8fab3fbf5a-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1375656" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/6314042c-924d-4928-b1fe-67a5c8697b66.jpg" alt="" width="1472" height="828" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/6314042c-924d-4928-b1fe-67a5c8697b66.jpg 1472w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/6314042c-924d-4928-b1fe-67a5c8697b66-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/6314042c-924d-4928-b1fe-67a5c8697b66-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/6314042c-924d-4928-b1fe-67a5c8697b66-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1472px) 100vw, 1472px" /></p>
